<div class="skills-section">
<div class="skills-grid">
<div class="skill-steps"><strong>Download the Game</strong>: Head over to the official Sonic Forever page and download the Easy Setup files.</div>
<div class="skill-steps"><strong>Create a Folder</strong>: After downloading, create a new folder and place the four files from the download inside it.</div>
<div class="skill-steps"><strong>Obtain the Game Files</strong>: You'll need the APK file of <em>Sonic the Hedgehog (2013)</em>. If you already have the <em>data.rsdk</em> file from a previous decompilation, you can use that instead of the APK.</div>
<div class="skill-steps"><strong>Run the Setup</strong>: Double-click the <code>S1F Setup.bat</code> file. The rest of the process will run automatically.</div>
<div class="skill-steps"><strong>Play the Game</strong>: Once everything is set up, simply launch the game by opening <code>SonicForever.exe</code>. Enjoy your enhanced <em>Sonic</em> experience!</div>
</div>
</div>
