<div class="skills-section">
<div class="skills-grid">
<div class="skill-steps"><strong>Download the Executable</strong>: Get the appropriate file for your device (Android APK or Switch NRO) from the official download link.</div>
<div class="skill-steps"><strong>Provide Game Files</strong>: Place the game files obtained through the Easy Setup into their respective folders on your device.</div>
<div class="skill-steps"><strong>Install the Game</strong>: Install the APK or NRO on your Android or Switch and follow any further setup instructions provided.</div>
</div>
