<h3>Stand-Alone Mod Version</h3>
<div class="description-section">For those who prefer using the mod-only version, Sonic Forever offers flexibility by allowing integration into existing mobile decompilations. This option is perfect for those who already have a Sonic decomp and only want to add the Forever mod.</div>
<h4>Mod-Only Version Installation Steps:</h4>
<div class="skills-section">
<div class="skills-grid">
<div class="skill-steps"><strong>Download the Mod-Only Files</strong>: Access the mod-only files through the official page and unzip them.</div>
