<div class="skill-steps"><strong>Replace Files</strong>: Extract the files and copy them into your existing Sonic Forever folder. Be sure to overwrite when prompted.</div>
<div class="skill-steps"><strong>Re-run Setup</strong>: Run the <code>S1F Setup.bat</code> file again to complete the update process.</div>
