<div class="skills-section">
<div class="skills-grid">
<div class="skill-steps"><strong>Download the Latest Mod Files</strong>: Get the updated files from the official website.</div>
<div class="skill-steps"><strong>Replace Old Files</strong>: Copy the updated files into your decomp mods folder.</div>
<div class="skill-steps"><strong>Activate Mod</strong>: Launch the game, enable the updated mod, and continue playing with the latest features.</div>
</div>
</div>
